  "title": "SALES AND MARKETING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>Permanently split shift – i.e. 10pm to 4am / 7am to 10am</p><p>Handling of perishable items – i.e. vegetables and fruits</p><p>Able to identify the quality of vegetables and fruits – i.e. selecting / rejecting / negotiating with suppliers</p><p>Able to justify pricing – regulating the price due to its perish-ability and limited-shelf-life (Must inform all concerned department accordingly, ie. cashier about the price adjustment i.e. discount and special offer).</p><p>Must have good knowledge about cold room storage, inventory check, stocking, etc </p><p>Overall-In-Charge for maintaining the cleanliness of the entire area – i.e. cold room, packing area, main sales walkway, etc </p><p>Must be customer oriented </p><p>Must be a team leader - the entire operation centered under your command</p><p>Hand phone must be on standby around the clock</p>",
